			<Body>
				<Text Type="text">
					&lt;p&gt;As you might expect, cans can impart a metallic flavor on some beer, but on the flip-side, they are much less prone to skunking. So if you're looking to store the beer for a while in a cool, dark place, I'd say bottle. However, if you plan on keeping it in a light place or outdoors, a can is probably your best bet.&lt;/p&gt;

				</Text>
			</Body>
